review_text: Some people call the Seribu Islands the Maldives van Java or the Maldives of Java Island. Because of its location close to the capital and affordable prices, the Thousand Islands are included in one of the governments tourism development priorities. Through the National Tourism Strategic Area (KSPN) program, the Seribu Islands are targeted to become world class tourism, on par with the Island of the Gods, Bali. The Ministry of Public Works and Public Housing (PUPR) carries out several programs such as fostering and developing residential infrastructure with sanitation arrangements in the Seribu Islands with the aim of  increasing the countrys foreign exchange as well as increasing income and empowering local communities. The program includes the development of buffer areas in the Seribu Islands KSPN which are located in two locations, namely Tidung Island and Untung Jawa Island, development of drainage in residential areas, waste, as well as construction of waste water infrastructure in areas on the islands, such as tourist toilets, international standard communal toilets, and TPS 3R (Reuse, Reduce and Recycle Waste Management Site). The Seribu Islands also have other supporting facilities such as a playground for children and watersport games such as jet ski, banana boat, donut boat, canoe. Apart from that, there is also a fishing arena, beach volleyball, futsal, swimming pool, table tennis, basketball court, tennis court, cycling and other facilities. For tourists who want to go on holiday to the Thousand Islands, it can be accessed via ports in several locations north of Jakarta, such as Marina Ancol Pier using a speedboat. Meanwhile, to use ships belonging to PT. Pelni, departure via Sunda Kelapa Port. Meanwhile, for those who want to use a traditional wooden boat at a more affordable price, you can go through Kali Adem Harbor in Muara Angke
review_translated_text: Kepulauan Seribu ada yang menjulukinya sebagai Maldives van Java atau Maldives dari Pulau Jawa. Karena lokasinya dekat dari ibukota dengan harga yang terjangkau, maka  Kepulauan Seribu masuk dalam salah satu prioritas pengembangan wisata oleh pemerintah. lewat program Kawasan Strategis Pariwisata Nasional (KSPN), Kepulauan Seribu ditargetkan menjadi wisata kelas dunia, sejajar dengan Pulau Dewata Bali. Kementerian Pekerjaan Umum dan Perumahan Rakyat (PUPR) melakukan beberapa program seperti pembinaan dan pengembangan infrastruktur pemukiman dengan penataan sanitasi di Kepulauan Seribu dengan tujuan  meningkatkan devisa negara serta peningkatan pendapatan dan pemberdayaan masyarakat lokal. Program tersebut meliputi  pengembangan daerah penyangga di KSPN Kepulauan Seribu yang berada di dua lokasi  yakni Pulau Tidung dan Pulau Untung Jawa, pengembangan  drainase kawasan pemukiman, persampahan, serta pembangunan  infrastruktur air limbah pada kawasan di kepulauan, seperti toilet wisata, MCK Komunal bertaraf internasional, serta TPS 3R (Tempat Pengelolaan Sampah Reuse, Reduce, dan Recycle). Kepulauan Seribu juga memiliki fasilitas pendukung lainnya seperti arena bermain untuk anak dan permainan watersport seperti jet ski, banana boat, donut boat, canoe. Selain itu, ada juga arena memancing, voli pantai, futsal, kolam renang, tenis meja, lapangan basket, lapangan tenis, bersepeda, dan fasilitas lainnya. Bagi wisatawan yang hendak berlibur ke Kepulauan Seribu, dapat diakses melalui pelabuhan yang berada di beberapa lokasi di utara Jakarta, seperti Dermaga Marina Ancol dengan menggunakan kapal cepat (speedboat). Sementara, untuk menggunakan kapal milik PT. Pelni, keberangkatannya melalui Pelabuhan Sunda Kelapa. Sedangkan bagi yang ingin mengunakan kapal kayu tradisional dengan harga yang lebih terjangkau, dapat melalui Pelabuhan Kali Adem di Muara Angke

review_text: This is my first time eating at Platinum. Ordered sirloin steak... when it arrived, it turned out it was a hot plate model that had to be cooked first like a pep**er lu*ch. I think it will immediately become holy  . What Im confused about is that there are fries there that are already cooked (the color is already a nice golden brown), along with green beans, carrots and corn that look like theyve been boiled. Then why do you put it on the hot plate too? It will cook and then overcook, aka it will burn hahaha As for the steak, it wasnt tender enough :(. Tbh, I cut the sirloin and it took a lot of effort, to the point where it was dry (maybe because I was pregnant, I got irritated easily). Yes, you can imagine how rich the steak would be because just cutting it made it dry like that hahaha. As for the sauce, I think its a little salty. Then for drinks, I just ordered mango smoothies because it reduces caffeine for pregnant women. And it turns out its really muaniiss, I dont know if its sweet from the mango, or the sugar, or... from the sweetened condensed milk (?) But I dont think its from the mango, as sweet as the mango is, it doesnt seem like that much. But its delicious, but its really sweet, please.
review_translated_text: Ini first time makan di platinum. Pesen sirloin steak... pas dateng, ternyata modelnya hot plate yg harus dimasak dulu kaya pep**er lu*ch gitu. Kirain yg langsung jadi kaya holy . Yg saya bingung, disitu kan ada kentang goreng yg emang base nya udah mateng (warna nya udah cakep golden brown gitu), sama buncis, wortel, jagung yg keliatannya udah direbus gitu. Terus kenapa ditaro juga di hot plate nya yak, kan jadinya ikut kemasak terus jadi overcook alias gosong wkwk Untuk steak nya kurang empuk :(. Tbh, saya motong sirloin nya perlu effort banget, sampe keringetan (mungkin karna lagi hamil juga sih jadi gampang gerah). Ya bisa dibayangin lah ya steak nya kaya gimana karna motong nya aja sampe keringetan gitu wkwk. Untuk sauce nya, menurut saya keasinan dikit. Terus untuk minumannya, saya pesen mango smoothies aja karna ngurangin kafein buat bumil. Dan ternyata muaniiss bangeett wkwk gak tau itu manis dari mangga nya kah, atau gula nya kah, atau... dari susu kental manis (?) Tapi kayanya kalo dari mangga nya nggak deh, se manis2 nya mangga kayanya gak sampe segitunya. Tapi enak sih, tapi kemanisan banget plis.

review_text: Location on the 2nd floor of Plaza Atrium Senen Near the elevator, near Miniso

Platinum in the atrium plaza is located on the 2nd floor.. Visited here during fasting last Tuesday. So at Platinum we dont accept bookings during fast breaking time. Only those whose personnel are complete can be let in. As a result, even though we were B5 and there were 3 new arrivals, we were brave enough to say that everything was complete. We were led to a table with 4 chairs. But it turned out that the 1 empty chair was immediately taken back by the lady. The lady said that next time someone comes, they wont promise a seat because thats the system. But luckily when our 2 friends came later, the waiters there still didnt bother looking for extra chairs After being a bit confused about what menu to choose, I finally decided to order the Hainanese spicy and sour chicken because I saw that it had tofu and it looked fresh from the picture. When you taste it, its not bad. The Hainanese rice is delicious, the tofu is delicious, the chicken is crunchy but the sauce is more dominant in sourness, it doesnt feel spicy at all. The only vegetable there is a leaf of mustard greens in the broth.. Theres nothing special about the Spiderman menu, except the usual sausages and French fries that are sold packaged in supermarkets.
review_translated_text: Platinum di atrium plaza ini terletak d lantai 2.. Berkunjung kemari saat bukber hri selasa lalu. Jaadi di platinum ini ga terima bookingan tampat selama waktu buka puasa. Siapa yg personilnya udah lengkap baru bisa dikasih masuk. Alhasil walaupun kami b5 dan yang baru datang 3 kami nekat aja bilang udah lengkap semua. Diantarkanlah kaami ke meja dengan 4 kursi. Tapi ternyata 1 kursi yg kosong itu langsung di ambil lagi sm mbaknya. Mbaknya bilang kl nanti ada yg datang lagi, mereka gbs janjiin kursi krn memang sistemnya begitu. Tp untungnya saat 2 teman kami datang belakangan, pelayan2 disana masih mau direpotkan untuk mencarikan kursi tambahan Setelah agak bingung mau pilih menu apa akhirnya memutuskan pesan ayam asam pedas hainan karena lihat ada tofunya dan kelihatan segar aja dari gambarnya. Saaat dicicip, lumayan lah ya. Nasi hainannya enak, tofunya enak, ayamnya crunchy tp untuk saucenya lebih dominan ke asamnya, pedasnya tidak terasa sama sekali. Sayurnya cuma terdapat selembar sawi di dalam kuah kaldu.. Kalau menu spiderman sih ga ada istimewanya cm sosis dan french fries biasa yg dijual kemasan di supermarket2 gitu.
